engChrName: Van and the others then proceeded through the hidden routes to the Blacklight District they had traveled through before.
engSearchText:
Van and the others then proceeded through the
hidden routes to the Blacklight District they had
traveled through before.
jpnChrName: ヴァンたちは何回か通ったことのある 黒芒街への裏ルートの一つを進んでいった。
jpnSearchText:
ヴァンたちは何回か通ったことのある
黒芒街への裏ルートの一つを進んでいった。

engChrName: Along the way, they approached a spare railway line that was rarely in use.
engSearchText:
Along the way, they approached a spare railway line
that was rarely in use.
jpnChrName: そんな中、普段は使われていない予備線路の 一画を通るエリアに差し掛かったところ──
jpnSearchText:
そんな中、普段は使われていない予備線路の
一画を通るエリアに差し掛かったところ──

engChrName: Just look at this...
engSearchText: Just look at this...
jpnChrName: これって……
jpnSearchText: これって……

engChrName: It's just like aboveground.
engSearchText: It's just like aboveground.
jpnChrName: 地上と同じような 状況になっていますね……
jpnSearchText:
地上と同じような
状況になっていますね……

engChrName: More underlings. Doesn't look like they're here 'cause of the demon spheres, though.
engSearchText:
More underlings. Doesn't look like they're here 'cause
of the demon spheres, though.
jpnChrName: やっぱり悪魔の眷族っぽいね。 魔球の影響は無さそうだけど。
jpnSearchText:
やっぱり悪魔の眷族っぽいね。
魔球の影響は無さそうだけど。

engChrName: More underlings. It would appear they have nothing to do with the demon spheres, however.
engSearchText:
More underlings. It would appear they have nothing
to do with the demon spheres, however.
jpnChrName: やはり悪魔の眷族どもか。 魔球の影響は無さそうだが。
jpnSearchText:
やはり悪魔の眷族どもか。
魔球の影響は無さそうだが。

engChrName: I see we've found more underlings, though the demon spheres seem uninvolved.
engSearchText:
I see we've found more underlings, though the demon
spheres seem uninvolved.
jpnChrName: やはり悪魔の眷族ですね。 魔球の影響は無さそうですが。
jpnSearchText:
やはり悪魔の眷族ですね。
魔球の影響は無さそうですが。

engChrName: Maybe, but that doesn't change the fact that there are some tough bastards roamin' around.
engSearchText:
Maybe, but that doesn't change the fact that there are
some tough bastards roamin' around.
jpnChrName: ああ、だがそれなりに 手強いのが顕れてやがる。
jpnSearchText:
ああ、だがそれなりに
手強いのが顕れてやがる。

engChrName: Whether we pick them off or slip by, keep your wits about you.
engSearchText:
Whether we pick them off or slip by, keep your wits
about you.
jpnChrName: 仕掛けるにせよ振り切るにせよ 気を抜くんじゃねえぞ。
jpnSearchText:
仕掛けるにせよ振り切るにせよ
気を抜くんじゃねえぞ。

engChrName: G-Got it!
engSearchText: G-Got it!
jpnChrName: ウ、了解（ウーラ）っ……！
jpnSearchText: ウ、了解（ウーラ）っ……！

engChrName: All we gotta do is bust some ass if they plan on getting in our way.
engSearchText:
All we gotta do is bust some ass if they plan on
getting in our way.
jpnChrName: ハッ……邪魔すんなら 叩き潰すのは変わらねぇだろ。
jpnSearchText:
ハッ……邪魔すんなら
叩き潰すのは変わらねぇだろ。

engChrName: Oh! The pattern's gone!
engSearchText: Oh! The pattern's gone!
jpnChrName: あ……紋様が 途切れてるみたいですっ！
jpnSearchText:
あ……紋様が
途切れてるみたいですっ！

engChrName: And those devils are nowhere to be found.
engSearchText: And those devils are nowhere to be found.
jpnChrName: クソったれな悪魔どもも いなさそうだな。
jpnSearchText:
クソったれな悪魔どもも
いなさそうだな。

engChrName: Yeah, I don't smell a thing. We should be safe going forward.
engSearchText:
Yeah, I don't smell a thing. We should be safe
going forward.
jpnChrName: ああ、匂いもねえし ここから先は大丈夫だろう。
jpnSearchText:
ああ、匂いもねえし
ここから先は大丈夫だろう。

engChrName: Understood.
engSearchText: Understood.
jpnChrName: ……承知しました。
jpnSearchText: ……承知しました。

engChrName: What's our next move, Van? Head straight for the Blacklight District?
engSearchText:
What's our next move, Van? Head straight for the
Blacklight District?
jpnChrName: どうする、ヴァン？ 一気に黒芒街へ向かおうか？
jpnSearchText:
どうする、ヴァン？
一気に黒芒街へ向かおうか？

engChrName: In that case, shall we head straight for the Blacklight District?
engSearchText:
In that case, shall we head straight for the
Blacklight District?
jpnChrName: ふむ、ならば一気に 黒芒街へ向かうか？
jpnSearchText:
ふむ、ならば一気に
黒芒街へ向かうか？

engChrName: Then shall we make way straight for the Blacklight District?
engSearchText:
Then shall we make way straight for the
Blacklight District?
jpnChrName: ふむ、ならば一気に 黒芒街へ向かいましょうか？
jpnSearchText:
ふむ、ならば一気に
黒芒街へ向かいましょうか？

engChrName: (I don't smell anything, so we should be good going forward.)
engSearchText:
(I don't smell anything, so we should be good
going forward.)
jpnChrName: （……匂いもねえし   ここから先は大丈夫だろう。）
jpnSearchText:
（……匂いもねえし
ここから先は大丈夫だろう。）

engChrName: Proceeding beyond this point will remove guests from the party.
engSearchText:
Proceeding beyond this point will remove guests from
the party.
jpnChrName: この先に向かうと同行している ゲストキャラがパーティから離脱します。
jpnSearchText:
この先に向かうと同行している
ゲストキャラがパーティから離脱します。
